            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">30. Leg pain<br />\nA 67-year-old woman suffered a fracture to her hip during a fall and undergoes a<br />\nsuccessful hip replacement. After 2 weeks, the patient complains of pain in her right<br />\nleg, particularly on movement. On examination, the leg is swollen below the knee,<br />\nerythematous and tender on palpation. The most appropriate management is:</p>"
